We offer both standard and customized transport and logistics solutions. Our services include Air, Ocean, Courier, Express and Special Services like Aircraft on Ground and Spare Parts Logistics. We were founded in 1981 as a subsidiary of SAS Cargo which is a member of SAS Group. Trust Forwarding is an independent full-service provider of freight forwarding services,

@BrianMTodd Hi, You can contact our live chat here https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj if you have a ticket number and we will find your booking reference for you. 
Kind regards, Bahare

@pulvardon Unfortunately I do not have a timeframe for when the baggage will be found. You could try calling Baggage Service to see if they have any updates. You can find their phone number here: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2 
Kind Regards, Natasha

data.text:
@LindbergMA Hi! If you are having issues contacting us on the phone I recommend contacting our live chat here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj That way they can try to help you find a more suitable alternative than the one you have. 
Kind Regards, Natasha

@PKashlikov You can find the phone number to SAS Baggage Service here: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2  If you call them they should be able to help you further. You can also add descriptions of your baggage here https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU that can help in the search. 
Kind Regards, Natasha

@pulvardon If you follow this link https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU you can trace your baggage. You can also add comments there about the baggage that can make it easier for Baggage Service to find. Once they have found it they will contact you about delivery. 
Kind Regards, Natasha

@NinjaofSwe I do not have information about exactly where your luggage is, since it is a different department that handles it. It is Baggage Service at the airport that handles these cases and traces the luggage. 
Kind Regards, Natasha

@hardynodak You can use your PIR-number from the report to trace your luggage here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU If you need to contact Baggage Service about delivery you can find their number here: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2 
Kind Regards, Natasha

@Avosetta54 If you haven't yet, please report the delayed baggage here https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 Once this is done you can use the PIR number to track your bag here https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU There you can also add descriptions of the bag that can help it easier be found. Kind Regards, Natasha

@Martin723ww Hi! I don't have any information about this at the moment. Make sure you allow SAS to send you emails with campaign offers and news to be informed if we decide to run a quadruple status points period this year. 
Kind Regards, Natasha

@athbalma The link with phone numbers Angelica sent is the most direct way to contact Baggage Service. Using this link https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU you should also be able to add descriptions about your luggage, that can make it easier for Baggage Service to find it. 
Kind Regards, Natasha

@NinjaofSwe Since you get the message "tracing continues" it sounds like Baggage Service are still searching for your bag, so this is why it does not say a location. Once your baggage has been found the status will be updated. 
Kind Regards, Natasha

@Marie_179 Hi! No, we do not allow combined baggage weights. If one of the bags weigh more than 23kg, even if the others weight less or you only check in 2, an overweight fee would need to be paid. 
Kind Regards, Natasha

@AlexW1864 SAS Baggage Service are working to reunite passengers with their luggage. Unfortunately we do not have a timeframe for this at the moment, and recommend waiting for Baggage Service to contact you once they have more information.
Kind Regards, Natasha

@PKashlikov Hi!
We are sorry to hear about your delayed bag!
The tracing of your bag will immediately start after you have reported it missing / delayed.
Once we have located your bag, you will be informed regarding delivery. 

Best regards, Angelica
